Answer: Pukul $12.15$
Explanation: >
  Waktu tempuh = Jarak $\div$ Kecepatan = $150 \div 50 = 3$ jam.
  Waktu tiba = Pukul $09.15 + 3$ jam = Pukul $12.15$.
