Answer: $15$ km
Explanation: >
  Jarak sebenarnya = Jarak peta $\times$ Skala = $3 \times 500.000 = 1.500.000$ cm.
  Karena $1$ km = $100.000$ cm, maka jarak sebenarnya = $\frac{1.500.000}{100.000} = 15$ km.
