Answer: $96$ $m^2$
Explanation: >
  Keliling = $2 \times (p + l) \Rightarrow 40 = 2 \times (p + 8) \Rightarrow p + 8 = 20 \Rightarrow p = 12$ m.
  Luas = $p \times l = 12 \times 8 = 96$ $m^2$.
