Answer: $375$ $m^2$
Explanation: >
  Keliling = $2 \times (p + l) \Rightarrow 80 = 2 \times (p + 15) \Rightarrow p + 15 = 40 \Rightarrow p = 25$ m.
  Luas = $p \times l = 25 \times 15 = 375$ $m^2$.
