  Volume setengah = $240$ liter ($dm^3$). Volume total = $240 \times 2 = 480$ $dm^3$.
  Volume = $p \times l \times t \Rightarrow 480 = 10 \times 6 \times t \Rightarrow 480 = 60 \times t \Rightarrow t = 8$ dm.
Options:
  - Text: $8$ dm
  - Text: $10$ dm
  - Text: $6$ dm
  - Text: $4$ dm
  - Text: $12$ dm
