Answer: Pukul $11.30$
Explanation: >
  Waktu tempuh = Jarak $\div$ Kecepatan = $140 \div 70 = 2$ jam.
  Total waktu = $2$ jam + $30$ menit istirahat = $2$ jam $30$ menit.
  Tiba = Pukul $09.00 + 2.30 = 11.30$.
Options:
  - Text: Pukul $11.30$
  - Text: Pukul $11.00$
  - Text: Pukul $12.00$
  - Text: Pukul $10.30$
  - Text: Pukul $12.30$
